methods.Enumeration elements(): Returns an enumeration of the values in this dictionary.
methods.V get(Object key): Returns the value to which the key is mapped in this dictionary.
methods.boolean isEmpty(): Tests if this dictionary maps no keys to value.
methods.Enumeration keys(): Returns an enumeration of the keys in this dictionary.
methods.V put(K key, V value): Maps the specified key to the specified value in this dictionary.
methods.V remove(Object key): Removes the key (and its corresponding value) from this dictionary.
methods.int size(): Returns the number of entries (distinct keys) in this dictionary.
